        "ACHIEVEMENT_PALADIN_TYPHOONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_DESCRIPTION": "Kiel Paladin, venku la ludon aux nuligu cxe Typhoon aux Eclipse.\n<color=#8888>(Kalkulas cxiun malfacilecon Typhoon aux pli alta)</color>",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_PALADIN_POISONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_ID_NAME": "Paladin: Her Disciple",
